title: Zombies Vs Cheerleaders (v1 + v2 & One-Shots) (2010 - 2014)
description:
Zombies Vs Cheerleaders (v1 + v2 & One-Shots) (2010 - 2014) (Complete)


A horror anthology set at a high school that has become the forefront for the battle of the human race during the zombie apocalypse that some science geek started, and nobody is there to fight except cheerleaders.

Contains

Zombies vs Cheerleaders v1 (01 - 07)

Zombies vs Cheerleaders v2 (01 - 03)

Hack-Slash Meets Zombies Vs Cheerleaders 001 (2011)(4 Covers) (Oroboros-CPS)

Rotten & Zombies vs Cheerleaders Flips Out 01 (2011)(Oroboros-Danger-CPS)

Zombies vs Cheerleaders - The Mis-Adventures of Becky And Bob 01 (2012)(Re-em-DCP-HD)

Zombies Vs Cheerleaders Geektacular 01 (2010)(4 Covers) (Legion-CPS)

Zombies Vs Cheerleaders Halloween Special(2014)(3 covers)(Digi-Hybrid)(TLK-EMPIRE-HD)
